Package edu.arizona.biosemantics.semanticmarkup.markupelement.description.ling.extract.lib

Defines the concrete process of XML markup extraction for morphological descriptions by chunk processors

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndChunkProcessor
    AndChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.AND
    AreaChunkProcessor
    AreaChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.AREA
    AverageChunkProcessor  
    BracketedChunkProcessor
    BracketedChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.BRACKETED
    CharacterNameChunkProcessor
    CharacterNameChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.CHARACTER_NAME
    CharacterStateChunkProcessor
    CharacterStateChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.CHARACTER_STATE
    ChromChunkProcessor
    ChromChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.CHROM * x= means basal number of chromosomes n= number of chromosomes in haploid state 2n= two sets of chromosomes n=2n= number of chromosomes in apogamous condition
    ChunkProcessorProvider
    ChunkProcessorProvider poses an IChunkProcessorProvider
    CommaChunkProcessor
    CommaChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.COMMA
    ComparativeValueChunkProcessor
    ComparativeValueChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.COMPARATIVE_VALUE

    ConstraintChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.CONSTRAINT
    CountChunkProcessor
    CountChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.COUNT
    DummyChunkProcessor
    DummyChunkProcessor does not do any processing.
    EosEolChunkProcessor
    EosEolChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.END_OF_LINE or ChunkType.END_OF_SUBCLAUSE
    MainSubjectOrganChunkProcessor
    MainSubjectOrganChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.MAIN_SUBJECT_ORGAN

    RatioChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.RATIO
    SBARChunkProcessor

    SomeDescriptionExtractor

    StateChunkProcessor

    ThanChunkProcessor

    ToChunkProcessor
    ToChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.TO
    ValuePercentageOrDegreeChunkProcessor
    ValuePercentageOrDegreeChunkProcessor processes chunks of ChunkType.VALUE_PERCENTAGE or ChunkType.VALUE_DEGREE
